  m_Text: 'Tis character use a LPSP pistol which was copied to the character with
    editor scripts. Including related SkinnedMeshRenderers and all bone hierachies.

    The
    bone Transforms are synchroinzed by FPSBoneSynchronizer.cs, and as the created
    weapon and bones are under character hierarchy, the baked animations will contain
    the weapon movement as well.

    This is just a demonstration. You probably
    need your own workflow to re-use LPSP weapons. Depending on your need.'
